reviewText: Karen Valentine and William DeVane have great chemistry in this movie.  It's one of my favorites for this reason.  It's not just a story of amnesia, serial killings or old fashioned husband wants me dead; it's a well put together thriller with all three aspects to keep your attention.  It's so well made that it doesn't have or need bad language and the violence level, believe it or not is little or none, except for what they leave to your imagination.
wonderful acting...suspenseful and exciting content. So glad to have this in my collection.
Karen Valentine gives a good performance.
This is a superior mystery and thriller.
One of my favorite movies....have watched it many times.
This is a fantastic movie! Don't hesitate to buy it.

I couldn't believe that I found this movie.  I first saw this on TV in the early 80s.  Remember when they actually had movies and and mini-series on TV.  I love this movie.  I am a big William Devane fan.  It definitely entertains and it's a little scary too.

It was a great movie which I enjoyed when showed on TV many years ago.  I wondered why with all the repeats that are shown on TV that they never show this movie.  I received it promptly in new condition.
I remember this movie from when I was younger and wanted to own it. It's a good movie with good actors.

Great TV movie with a surprise ending.  Anyone who likes whodunits will enjoy this film.

I remember this movie when it first appeared on tv and wish our current tv lineup included more of mysteries and less of reality shows.

I highly recommend this movie.
